# Editing rules

- Editing `rules/*.md` affects **all** future `install.sh` runs—bump guidance carefully and keep frontmatter generation logic in `install.sh` aligned.
- Skills should stay self-contained with runnable scripts where applicable; test paths on macOS/Linux.
